Indiana Fever guard Caitlin Clark shined early at the LPGA Annika pro-am. Clark paired with Nelly Korda and showed off her swing with a 35-foot putt.
Kai Trump improved by eight strokes on her second day at the Annika tournament, crediting a more peaceful mindset for better performance in her LPGA debut.
Miami women's golf coach Jim Garren praised his recruit, Kai Trump, ahead of her making her LPGA debut as a sponsorship exemption at The Annika.
President Donald Trump's granddaughter Kai Trump shot 13-over 83 in her LPGA tour debut at The Annika in Florida, finishing last in the 108-player field.
Professional golfer Phil Mickelson endorsed Steve Hilton's gubernatorial campaign after the GOP candidate outlined plans to lower California gas prices through local drilling.
High school senior Kai Trump will make her professional debut at The Annika in Belleair, Florida, showcasing her talent among LPGA stars before heading to the University of Miami.
President Donald Trump’s granddaughter, Kai, will debut at The ANNIKA LPGA event in Florida, earning praise from Annika Sorenstam and advice from her grandfather and Tiger Woods.
Golf influencer Paige Spiranac broke down over hateful messages received during the $1 million Internet Invitational, revealing deep insecurities about fitting in and being liked.
LIV Golf is expanding to 72 holes for the first time, as part of "a path forward."
Comedian Becky Robinson's pandemic-born "Entitled Housewife" character blew up on social media, earning millions of views, and helped launch her 'Member's Only' tour.
Kai Trump, the president’s granddaughter, will make her LPGA Tour debut at the ANNIKA in Belleair, Florida, fulfilling her dream of competing alongside the game’s top players.
Charles Howell III from Augusta, Georgia, is no stranger to playing a tournament with the Masters on his mind.
19-year-old Sewanee Tigers golfer Niel Phillips joins 'Fox & Friends First' to describe the 'shock and denial' he felt after achieving the feat at the Chick-fil-A Invitational in Rome, Georgia.
A Florida jury awarded Jack Nicklaus $50 million in damages after finding his former company spread false information about LIV Golf negotiations and his mental fitness.
Phil Mickelson, a staunch President Donald Trump supporter, made a social media post appearing to mock nationwide "No Kings Day" protests against GOP priorities.
Caitlin Clark was named a Gainbridge ambassador for The Annika LPGA event. She appeared in the 2024 pro-am event. This year's tournament is scheduled to begin Nov. 12.
In an interview with Fox News Digital, Kai Trump explained that playing golf with her grandfather, President Donald Trump, is simply just another day for her.
PGA Tour star Rory McIlroy said fan altercations at Bethpage Black overshadowed Team Europe's historic 15-13 Ryder Cup victory over Team USA last month.
Tiger Woods had lumbar disk surgery for back problems, a continuation of health struggles that have limited him to poor finishes since his 2019 Masters victory.
Phil Mickelson shared his reaction to conservative activist Charlie Kirk receiving the Presidential Medal of Freedom after Kirk's assassination in Utah last month.
Sports Illustrated Swimsuit model Jena Sims revealed in a heartbreaking social media post on Monday she suffered a miscarriage at 16 weeks
PGA Tour golfer Vince Whaley was caught in a frightening moment on Sunday as he was trying to hit his ball out of murky water. An alligator was staring him down.
Five Iron Golf co-founder Mike Doyle joins 'Fox & Friends Weekend' to discuss his company and offer tips for improving your swing.
PGA of America CEO Derek Sprague apologized to Rory McIlroy and wife Erica after inappropriate fan behavior during Team Europe's Ryder Cup victory at Bethpage Black.
Comedian Heather McMahan denied leading hostile chants at the Ryder Cup Saturday that led to her stepping down from her role as a host.
Team USA icon Paul Azinger called out Rory McIlroy for condemning Ryder Cup fan behavior while directing profanity at spectators at Bethpage Black.
An NYPD detective was suspended without pay after pretending to be part of President Donald Trump's detail at the 2025 Ryder Cup at Bethpage Black this past weekend.
Phil Mickelson called for judicial accountability after Stephen Federico's emotional testimony about his daughter Logan's murder in North Carolina.
Golf influencer Paige Spiranac slammed Ryder Cup fans for crossing the line with their heckling of Rory McIlroy and other European players.
Rory McIlroy endured relentless heckling from hostile Bethpage Black crowds during the Ryder Cup but had the last laugh as Europe beat the U.S. 15-13.
